WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.010 --> 00:00:01.080 
Angelica is a mother.

2
00:00:01.410 --> 00:00:02.220 
She has three children.

3
00:00:02.830 --> 00:00:03.740 
She goes to the doctor.

4
00:00:04.330 --> 00:00:06.120 
The doctor says, You are sick.

5
00:00:07.110 --> 00:00:08.380 
You have cancer.

6
00:00:09.210 --> 00:00:11.580 
You can live for three more months.

7
00:00:12.730 --> 00:00:13.760 
Angelica is sad.

8
00:00:14.010 --> 00:00:14.640 
She cries.

9
00:00:15.330 --> 00:00:17.300 
She thinks, I want to be happy.

10
00:00:17.630 --> 00:00:19.140 
I want to be with my children.

11
00:00:19.790 --> 00:00:22.160 
Angelica says, I want to eat good food.

12
00:00:22.730 --> 00:00:24.320 
She goes to a restaurant with her children.

13
00:00:24.930 --> 00:00:25.720 
She eats chicken.

14
00:00:26.330 --> 00:00:27.080 
She eats meat.

15
00:00:27.710 --> 00:00:28.540 
She drinks juice.

16
00:00:28.550 --> 00:00:32.940 
Her son says, Mom, this is too much.

17
00:00:34.170 --> 00:00:37.020 
Angelica says, Let me eat.

18
00:00:37.310 --> 00:00:38.740 
I want to be happy.

19
00:00:39.410 --> 00:00:41.840 
She says, Thank you, God, for my life.

20
00:00:42.730 --> 00:00:43.600 
Three months pass.

21
00:00:44.250 --> 00:00:45.400 
Angelica is still alive.

22
00:00:46.070 --> 00:00:46.920 
She goes to the park.

23
00:00:47.410 --> 00:00:48.340 
She plays with her children.

24
00:00:48.950 --> 00:00:49.440 
They laugh.

25
00:00:49.530 --> 00:00:50.160 
They are happy.

26
00:00:50.610 --> 00:00:53.880 
Her son says, Mom, you are not sick.

27
00:00:54.530 --> 00:00:55.360 
Angelica smiles.

28
00:00:55.870 --> 00:00:59.700 
She says, Maybe the sickness is not here now.

29
00:01:00.450 --> 00:01:01.660 
Angelica goes to the doctor again.

30
00:01:02.110 --> 00:01:05.960 
The doctor says, You are okay now.

31
00:01:06.790 --> 00:01:08.180 
Angelica is very happy.

32
00:01:08.510 --> 00:01:09.820 
She says, Thank you, God.

33
00:01:10.090 --> 00:01:11.420 
Her family is happy too.

34
00:01:11.950 --> 00:01:12.520 
They hug her.

35
00:01:13.370 --> 00:01:15.580 
They say, Let's help people.

36
00:01:16.350 --> 00:01:18.260 
Angelica and her children give food to people.

37
00:01:18.910 --> 00:01:19.940 
They give clothes too.

38
00:01:20.410 --> 00:01:21.280 
They are happy.

39
00:01:21.750 --> 00:01:22.740 
They help many people.

40
00:01:23.430 --> 00:01:25.680 
Angelica says, Helping is good.

41
00:01:25.990 --> 00:01:26.980 
I feel good.

42
00:01:27.850 --> 00:01:29.260 
Now Angelica has grandchildren.

43
00:01:30.070 --> 00:01:32.840 
They run, they play, they laugh.

44
00:01:33.490 --> 00:01:34.380 
Angelica smiles.

45
00:01:35.150 --> 00:01:37.000 
She says, Family is love.

46
00:01:37.230 --> 00:01:38.280 
She is happy every day.

